name: iMIX Sticker Pack
description:
I started iMIX at the beginning of the year & it stands for ([M]otivate • [I]nspire • BM[X]). At first, it was just going to be a BMX Crew which had a good amount of my friends representing it, who all happen to be awesome riders. Our goal was to show the world what we love to do. To motivate & inspire people to find a passion in life that they love. A passion that defines who they are. But then, I got to thinking & decided that it would be better if iMIX was something that anyone & everyone can represent. So instead of just being defined as a crew, iMIX will now have a crew & family within it. Also, iMIX can be a lifestyle & way of life. As a way to better yourself & those around you through BMX, by motivating & inspiring them. So, if you ride BMX, motivate & inspire others, then you should definitely rep iMIX. Even if you don’t ride BMX but are still down with the cause, then you can definitely rep too. iMIX will still have the same goal to motivate & inspire people to find a passion in life, but now anyone & everyone can represent instead of just the original crew. Check out the iMIX Facebook Page, give it a like, order some stickers & get to reppin’. 
- Corey Furmage

www.facebook.com/imixcrew

Our iMIX Stickers are made from high quality vinyl with UV-cured inks, which are scratch-proof, fade-proof & weatherproof. I put a penny next to the stickers for a size comparison.

iMIX Sticker Pack includes a mix of ten stickers for $1.

*USA ONLY
